OL,3,CMarathon effort in memory of
OL,4,Ccolleagues to find journalist with
OL,5,C'fire in belly'
OL,7,FGeoff Hill was Editor of ITV News and
OL,8,Fdied aged 52 after being diagnosed
OL,9,Fwith leukemia. Bernard Cole was
OL,10,FProgramme Editor of ITV News At Ten
OL,11,Fand died suddenly of a heart attack.
OL,12,FHealth and Science Editor Emily Morgan
OL,13,Fpassed away after being diagnosed with
OL,14,Flung cancer. Picture Editor and Media
OL,15,FManager Lim Ho died after a sudden
OL,16,Fillness. And Westminster Camera
OL,17,FOperator and Video Editor Chris
OL,18,FKnapman passed away with his family by
OL,19,Fhis side after a short illness.
