OL,3,CMarathon effort in memory of
OL,4,Ccolleagues to find journalist with
OL,5,C'fire in belly'
OL,7,FJoel Hills said each adored working in
OL,8,Fbroadcasting and he wanted to help a
OL,9,Fbudding journalist with "fire in their
OL,10,Fbelly" get into the profession.
OL,12,F"Graduates from Cardiff's School of
OL,13,FJournalism, Media and Culture populate
OL,14,Fnewsrooms across the UK," Joel said.
OL,16,F"A Masters from Cardiff can be the
OL,17,Ffirst step in a wonderful career, I
OL,18,Fknow because I trained there, but it
OL,19,Fis also a huge financial commitment,"
OL,20,Fhe added.
